wdi2-SE.XPD.TOTL.GD.ZS.def: General government expenditure on education (current, capital, and transfers) is expressed as a percentage of GDP. It includes expenditure funded by transfers from international sources to government. General government usually refers to local, regional and central governments.
wdi2-SE.XPD.TOTL.GD.ZS.name: Government expenditure on education
wdi2-SE.XPD.TOTL.GD.ZS.source: UNESCO Institute for Statistics (http://uis.unesco.org/). Data as of September 2020.
